Find details of a UK design registered with the Intellectual Property Office.

You need to know the design number or the design owner’s name.
chunks.plain_content:
Find a registered design
Find details of a UK design registered with the Intellectual Property Office.
You need to know the design number or the design owner’s name.

chunks.html_content: If you do not know the design number or the design owner’s name, use the Designview search tool.
chunks.plain_content:
Find a registered design
If you do not know the design number or the design owner’s name, use the Designview search tool.

chunks.html_content:
You can also use the Designview search tool to search for designs registered in the UK by the:

  • World Intellectual Property Organization
  • European Union Intellectual Property Office

There’s a different process to search for:

  • designs registered in Jersey
  • designs registered in Guernsey
